import { parse } from "https://esm.sh/@progfay/scrapbox-parser@7.2.0";
declare const text: string;
const blocks = parse(text);
const mecab = blocks.flatMap((block) => {
if (block.type !== "line") return [];
const indent = " ".repeat(block.indent);
return [
`[${indent}]\tSCRAPBOX_INDENT`,
...block.nodes.flatMap((node) => {
console.log(node);
switch (node.type) {
case "plain":
return [node.text];
case "link":
return [`${node.raw}\tSCRAPBOX_LINK`];
case "icon":
return [`${node.raw}\tSCRAPBOX_ICON`];
default:
return [];
"[NEWLINE]\tNEWLINE",
] as `${string}\t${string}`[];
console.log(mecab.join("\n"));
